{"tid":2295104,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"英國電話預約NI對話懶人包","createTime":"2020-11-21T13:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T22:59:25.000Z","uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bec21b18331b5634b3f25feae749e4ebc0643b","tid":2295104,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://albaenglish.co.uk/blog/how-get-your-nino\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Falbaenglish.co.uk%2Fblog%2Fhow-get-your-nino&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b3be4955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://albaenglish.co.uk/blog/how-get-your-nino</a><br />\n<br />\n首先唔係全英國都lock down<br />\n就算係England <br />\n解封後 你點都要打電話去job centre預約<br />\n佢如果話叫你填表就得，呢個係後話<br />\n<br />\n不過Job Centre聽電話嘅職員<br />\n受訓過程係有個表  指明佢要講啲咩，同埋可以答啲咩<br />\n個對話其實全機械式 <br />\n我有佢地份training material不過唔up上黎了<br />\n<br />\n呢個網站教埋你點答<br />\n英文唔好嘅人自己望吓啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（注意： 人地個website 係2015年)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 下亞妮陰道 好快會喺下面洗板話我阻住啲人LOTR去英國"},{"pid":"eb7a6700ae92a0fbb62faa400fc428f6cf8bb878","tid":2295104,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"同埋注意<br />\nNI 係無所謂快証<br />\n就算你搵agent幫你搞<br />\n佢地都只係同普通人一樣代你狂打電話去job centre<br />\n唔好俾人呃"},{"pid":"1fcdb5f8e720c379b187b99198fbeb93db5432f1","tid":2295104,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43acf635e7e1440e2d0c3cca923391dbc91537b7","tid":2295104,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T22:59:25.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}